sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'; import {Container,Button} from '../../globalStyles' import { InfoSec,InfoRow,InfoColumn,TextWrapper,TopLine,Heading,Subtitle,ImgWrapper,Img} from './InfoSection.elements'; function InfoSection({ primary, lightBg, topLine, lightText, lightTopLine, lightTextDesc, headline, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, imgStart, start }){ return( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ); } export default InfoSection;
